Architecture diagram: Hybrid Search flow. Query splits into two paths: TOP PATH - Vector Search: Query -> Embedding -> HNSW Index (graph visualization) -> Cosine Similarity Scores. BOTTOM PATH - BM25 Search: Query -> Tokenization -> Inverted Index -> BM25 Scores. MERGE: Weighted Combination (0.7 * Vector + 0.3 * BM25) -> Reranked Results. PostgreSQL/pgvector branding, technical diagram style.